headline: GE HealthCare unveils Pristina Recon DL for mammography – deep learning image reconstruction technology delivering clearer image quality
summary: CHICAGO, November 26, 2025--GE HealthCare (Nasdaq: GEHC) announced today that it has received FDA Premarket Authorization for Pristina Recon DL, an advanced 3D mammography image reconstruction technology. Powered by deep learning, Pristina Recon DL sets a new standard in image definition and sharpness.
